data.description: Enjoy one level living in this fabulous "Coastal Industrial" themed fully updated home in beautiful Copperleaf. Your mind will be blown by the modern high end finishes the owner's have selected that relay an easy relaxed feeling almost like you are staying at a luxury AirBnb by the beach.  From the moment you walk in feel the amazing energy this home offers like all the finishes blending perfectly together.  From gorgeous wide plank luxury vinyl floors throughout, custom tall craftsman style trim and baseboards, white no fade plantation shutters, a beautiful custom fireplace mantel & tile surround, built in dual work stations, black hardware, entertainer's dream kitchen with double ovens & granite countertops, huge walk in shower with full slab no seam quartz walls and large walk in closet.  Head down to the basement to find 1,854 sf of limitless possibilities where finishes could easily include adding 2 more beds, another bath, rec room & storage. The relaxing backyard features a private covered patio, extended concrete patio with firepit area & nice space for the kids and dogs.  This home is in a great location within Copperleaf just a few blocks from the pool and clubhouse & directly across from Western Park. Cherry Creek Schools! This home truly stands out from all others for sale in Copperleaf.
